translate-magic-help: Ye can owerset byordiair pages aliases, magic wairds n namespace names. Byordinair page aliases n magic wairds can hae multiple owersets. Owersets ar separated bi ae comma (,). Namespaces can yinlie hae the yin owerset. Owersetin the waurk tauk namespace $1 tauk micht be compleecatit. $1 is replaced wi the waurk sitename (fer example {{ns:project_talk}}). Gif it's na possible in yer leid tae form ae valit expression wioot chyngin the sitename, please lat us know oan [[Support]]. Ye need tae be aen owerseter tae hain chynges. Chynges ar na hained ontil ye clap the hain button ablo.
